game.name: Motor Model Dressup
game.description:
Hey ladies! This cute blonde girl is a very popular model of the city. She has to perform an advertisement to promote a new car model of a popular auto company. The girl looks pretty excited for this new ad assignment, but is unable to decide what to put on to look fabulous on the leading motor show. She has approached you for quick fashion advice. Would you be able to guide her to dress up with cool outfits? Join Motor Model Dress Up and be prepared to get the girl ready for the leading motor show tonight! 

This beautiful princess has a wide experience of attending many popular motor shows. But this show is a bit different. Her jaw-dropping look can help the lady to grab some more beneficial ad deals in future. Start with giving your lady a nice hairstyle and then choose a strapless purple one piece dress and pair it with purple leggings with transparent circles and a pair of matching sandal. Give your girl a perfect necklace and earrings in this one of the best HTML5 dressing games! 

She will also love beautiful in yellow dress with red color bra and combine it with a pair of long shoes. You can also dress her up with a pink short dress and pair it with a pair of matching sandals and elegant jewelry pieces. Once you mix and match all the items, click the show button to see the final result. Click on the Reset button to start your fun dress-up game again! If you like this game, feel free to try out huge collection of free dress-up games to kill your time without download.
